  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Hariom Atta & Spices IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->1155000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->5.54<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹48 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->3000<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->May 16, 2024</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->May 21, 2024</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->NSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Hariom Atta & Spices IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Hariom Atta & Spices IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO opens on May 16, 2024 and closes on May 21, 2024.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Hariom Atta & Spices IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->3000</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹1,44,000</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Hariom Atta & Spices IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Hariom Atta & Spices IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Wednesday, May 22, 2024<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Thursday, May 23, 2024<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/hariom-atta-spices-ipo/1729/\" title=\"Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO Allotment Status\">Hariom Atta &amp; Spices IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
